'''亚美尼亚-以色列关系'''是[[亚美尼亚|亚美尼亚]]和[[以色列|以色列]]之间的双边关系。从1993年到2007年，以色列驻格鲁吉亚大使馆为亚美尼亚提供服务。1996年，索拉克·蒙坚被任命为亚美尼亚驻耶路撒冷名誉领事。11年后，以色列驻亚美尼亚大使馆迁址到耶路撒冷。2010年10月，什米尔·梅罗姆被任命为以色列驻亚美尼亚大使。<ref name="Armenia-Israel Bilateral Relations">{{cite news|title=Bilateral Relations|url=http://mfa.am/en/country-by-country/il/|publisher=Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Armenia|access-date=2013-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806141056/http://mfa.am/en/country-by-country/il/|archive-date=2017-08-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>阿曼·梅尔科尼安2012年被任命为亚美尼亚驻以色列大使，在[[开罗|开罗]]有住所。<ref>{{cite web|last=Chernamorian|first=Artiom|url=http://www.friends-of-armenia.org/armenia-already-has-an-ambassador-in-israel|title=Armenia Already Has An Ambassador In Israel|work=Friends of Armenia|date=2012-05-11|access-date=2013-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030120236/http://www.friends-of-armenia.org/armenia-already-has-an-ambassador-in-israel|archive-date=2014-10-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>当年10月，梅尔科尼安向以色列总统[[西蒙·佩雷斯|西蒙·佩雷斯]]递交了国书。<ref>{{cite web|last=Cashman|first=Greer|url=http://www.jpost.com/Diplomacy-and-Politics/New-Egyptian-envoy-Were-committed-to-peace|title=New Egyptian envoy: We're committed to peace|work=[[The_Jerusalem_Post|The Jerusalem Post]]|date=2012-10-17|access-date=2013-08-09|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207113552/https://www.jpost.com/Diplomacy-and-Politics/New-Egyptian-envoy-Were-committed-to-peace|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年9月21日，亚美尼亚宣布将在以色列开设大使馆。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/269153|title=Armenia to open embassy in Israel|website=Israel National News|language=en|access-date=2019-10-03|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202094158/https://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/269153|dead-url=no}}</ref>尽管两国关系友好，但在[[2020年纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争|2020年的纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争]]中，由于以色列向亚美尼亚的敌人阿塞拜疆提供武器，亚美尼亚撤回了驻以色列大使后，两国关系恶化。<ref>{{cite news |title=Armenia withdraws ambassador to Israel over Azerbaijan arms sales |url=https://www.middleeasteye.net/news/armenia-withdraws-ambassador-israel-over-azerbaijan-arms-sales |access-date=2020-10-02 |publisher=middle east eye |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127192922/https://www.middleeasteye.net/news/armenia-withdraws-ambassador-israel-over-azerbaijan-arms-sales |dead-url=no }}</ref>
== 外交关系 ==
自1991年亚美尼亚从苏联独立以来，以色列和亚美尼亚一直保持着外交关系。<ref name="Armenia-Israel Bilateral Relations"/>1993年至2007年，亚美尼亚驻以色列外交使团设在格鲁吉亚，但索拉克·蒙坚在1996年被任命为亚美尼亚驻耶路撒冷名誉领事。<ref name="Armenia-Israel Bilateral Relations"/>

亚美尼亚人对以色列进行了几次高层访问。亚美尼亚前总统[[罗伯特·科恰良|罗伯特·科恰良]]于2000年1月访问以色列，会见了包括以色列前总理埃胡德·巴拉克在内的以色列高级官员。两国承诺加强关系，并签署了卫生和双边投资协议。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ncsj.org/Armenia.shtml |title=Advocates on Behalf of Jews in Russia, Ukraine, the Baltic States and Eurasia - Armenia |accessdate=2021-01-20 |archive-date=2011-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706153235/http://www.ncsj.org/Armenia.shtml |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2003年，所有亚美尼亚人的天主教徒领袖卡列柯二世拜访了以色列的德系犹太人首席拉比约纳·梅茨格。梅茨格接受了卡列柯在2005年访问亚美尼亚的邀请，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.armeniandiaspora.com/forum/showthread.php?t=26904 |title=Ara Abrahamian called to develop Armenia-Israel relations |accessdate=2021-01-20 |archive-date=2007-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927184444/http://www.armeniandiaspora.com/forum/showthread.php?t=26904 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他的访问包括参观位于埃里温的种族灭绝纪念馆。<ref name="armenianchurch.org">{{cite web|url=http://www.armenianchurch.org/index.jsp?sid=3&nid=421&y=2005&m=10&d=22&lng=en|title=The Armenian Church|work=armenianchurch.org|accessdate=2021-01-20|archive-date=2018-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118172033/https://www.armenianchurch.org/index.jsp?sid=3&nid=421&y=2005&m=10&d=22&lng=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>在纪念仪式上，他正式承认了亚美尼亚的种族灭绝。<ref name="ym">{{cite web|title=World Jewish Congress: Israeli Chief Rabbi says killing of Armenians in 1915 was genocide|url=http://www.worldjewishcongress.org/en/news/5737/israeli_chief_rabbi_says_killing_of_armenians_in_1915_was_genocide|accessdate=2021-01-20|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215005738/http://www.worldjewishcongress.org/en/news/5737/israeli_chief_rabbi_says_killing_of_armenians_in_1915_was_genocide|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年，什米尔·梅罗姆（居住在耶路撒冷的以色列驻亚美尼亚大使）表示，以色列愿意尽快向亚美尼亚提供免签证待遇，首先是外交护照持有者。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.arminfo.am/index.cfm?objectid=709093A0-131D-11E4-BB4C0EB7C0D21663|title=Arminfo: Shmuel Meirom: Israel is willing to contribute of its experience in the field of economy, but it cannot force Israeli business to invest in Armenia|work=arminfo.am|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730152731/http://www.arminfo.am/index.cfm?objectid=709093A0-131D-11E4-BB4C0EB7C0D21663}}</ref>

两国关系在2020年9月恶化。为了回应以色列在2020年纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫冲突中对阿塞拜疆的持续军事支持，亚美尼亚召回了其驻以色列大使。<ref> https://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2020-10-01/armenia-says-it-recalls-ambassador-from-israel-over-arms-sales-to-azerbaijan</ref>[[阿尔察赫共和国|阿尔察赫共和国]]总统的[[阿拉伊克·阿鲁秋尼扬|阿拉伊克·阿鲁秋尼扬]]指责以色列参与了“种族灭绝”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://jewishnews.timesofisrael.com/armenian-leader-accuses-israel-of-aiding-genocide-against-his-people/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2021-01-20 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125024952/https://jewishnews.timesofisrael.com/armenian-leader-accuses-israel-of-aiding-genocide-against-his-people/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

